items.title: France seizes suspected Russian 'shadow fleet' oil tanker in the Mediterranean
items.description: The vessel, named Grinch, was stopped by the French navy as it travelled through waters between Spain and Morocco.

items.title: What we know about Trump's  'framework of future deal' over Greenland
items.description: Denmark and Greenland have made it clear they will not relinquish sovereignty of the world's largest island.

items.title: German nurse jailed for murders could be linked to 100 more deaths
items.description: Prosecutors are reviewing dozens more suspected deaths linked to a former palliative care nurse.

items.title: 'It's all about the land': Zelensky says Ukraine to talk to US and Russia
items.description: The meeting came as US envoy Steve Witkoff headed to Moscow for a meeting with Russia's Vladimir Putin.

items.title: ICE detains 5-year-old and father in Minnesota, lawyer says
items.description: The boy was taken along with his father, the lawyer and school officials say. ICE says it was not targeting the boy.
